OL,3,CCompany fined after worker suffers
OL,4,Cbrain injury while installing solar
OL,5,Cpanels
OL,7,FA company has been fined #28,000 after
OL,8,Fa worker sustained a severe brain
OL,9,Finjury while installing solar panels
OL,10,Fon the roof of a house, leaving him
OL,11,Funable to walk or talk.
OL,13,FThe man, who was employed by
OL,14,FEveryone's Energy UK Limited, was
OL,15,Fworking at an address on Pentland
OL,16,FAvenue, Thornbury, on 4 July 2022,
OL,17,Fwhen he fell three metres off a ladder.
