OL,3,CCompany fined after worker suffers
OL,4,Cbrain injury while installing solar
OL,5,Cpanels
OL,7,FThe 41-year-old landed at the foot of
OL,8,Fthe ladder and suffered a fractured
OL,9,Fskull, leading to a severe brain
OL,10,Finjury which has left him unable to
OL,11,Fwalk or talk.
OL,13,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,14,FSafety Executive (HSE) identified a
OL,15,Fseries of failings by the company.
OL,17,FIt found that Everyone's Energy UK
OL,18,FLimited had failed to properly plan,
OL,19,Fmanage and monitor working at height.
