OL,3,CCompany fined after worker suffers
OL,4,Cbrain injury while installing solar
OL,5,Cpanels
OL,7,FInspectors also found the company had
OL,8,Fnot provided adequate scaffolding
OL,9,Faround the roof and there was no
OL,10,Fappropriate means of getting materials
OL,11,Fonto the roof.
OL,13,FHSE Inspector Ian Whittles said it was
OL,14,Fa "serious incident (which) could have
OL,15,Fbeen avoided if the employer had acted
OL,16,Fto identify and control the risks
OL,17,Finvolved."
