OL,3,CCompany fined after worker suffers
OL,4,Cbrain injury while installing solar
OL,5,Cpanels
OL,7,FEveryone's Energy UK Limited, based in
OL,8,FHertfordshire, pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fbreaching Regulation 4(1) of the Work
OL,10,Fat Height Regulations 2005.
OL,12,FThe company was fined #28,000 and
OL,13,Fordered to pay around #6,000 in costs
OL,14,Fduring a hearing at Bristol
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on 12 March 2024.
